public static enum PlayConstants.DefaultId
extends java.lang.Enum<PlayConstants.DefaultId>
implements CellId

HitNoWhere is used as the code for "nothing hit yet". Other values are used by various stock widgets and buttons, such as the VCR controls and the "done" button. Use the interface CellId to refer to any id
